bin/omarchy-launch-screensaver
  â””â”€ Main launcher script
  â””â”€ Handles multi-monitor setup
  â””â”€ Detects terminal type

bin/omarchy-cmd-screensaver
  â””â”€ Screensaver execution logic
  â””â”€ Runs TTE in a loop
  â””â”€ Monitors for input/exit

config/hypr/hypridle.conf
  â””â”€ Idle detection configuration
  â””â”€ 150 second timeout
  â””â”€ Triggers launcher

