 UNDERSTANDING THE CODE FLOW
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

USER IDLE (150s)
    â†“
HYPRIDLE DETECTS
    â†“
CALLS: screensaver-launch
    â†“
    â”œâ”€ Checks if TTE installed
    â”œâ”€ Checks if already running
    â”œâ”€ Gets list of monitors
    â”‚
    â””â”€ FOR EACH MONITOR:
         â”œâ”€ Focus monitor
         â”œâ”€ Launch fullscreen terminal
         â””â”€ Execute: screensaver-cmd
              â†“
              â”œâ”€ Set black background
              â”œâ”€ Hide cursor
              â”‚
              â””â”€ LOOP FOREVER:
                   â”œâ”€ Run TTE with random effect
                   â”œâ”€ Monitor for keyboard input
                   â”œâ”€ Check if window still focused
                   â””â”€ Exit if input detected
                        â†“
                        â”œâ”€ Show cursor
                        â”œâ”€ Kill TTE
                        â””â”€ Close all screensaver windows


